1
00:00:11,930 --> 00:00:12,800
General.

2
00:00:13,030 --> 00:00:14,360
Madam is here to see you.

3
00:00:24,630 --> 00:00:26,430
What happened, Lu Jingxing?

4
00:00:27,730 --> 00:00:28,600
You are here.

5
00:00:28,600 --> 00:00:29,630
It's nothing serious.

6
00:00:29,630 --> 00:00:30,960
You are on death row.

7
00:00:30,960 --> 00:00:32,619
How can it be nothing serious?

8
00:00:34,030 --> 00:00:36,330
His Majesty has always valued me as a loyal subject.

9
00:00:36,330 --> 00:00:38,630
But this time I got involved in the late Emperor's edict,

10
00:00:38,630 --> 00:00:40,030
and favored the Minister's Manor.

11
00:00:40,030 --> 00:00:41,430
His Majesty is disappointed in me.

12
00:00:41,430 --> 00:00:42,830
He relieved me of my military power

13
00:00:42,830 --> 00:00:44,830
and put me in prison awaiting trial.

14
00:00:48,930 --> 00:00:50,330
It was my fault.

15
00:00:50,460 --> 00:00:52,230
I dragged you down after all.

16
00:00:54,400 --> 00:00:55,100
Take this.

17
00:00:55,230 --> 00:00:56,330
What is this?

18
00:00:56,930 --> 00:00:58,190
Your appeal petition?

19
00:00:59,560 --> 00:01:00,660
A letter of divorce.

20
00:01:00,660 --> 00:01:02,730
Lu Jingxing, you want to divorce me?

21
00:01:04,129 --> 00:01:05,960
Now Minister Shen's name has been cleared.

22
00:01:05,960 --> 00:01:08,700
You are the precious eldest daughter of the Minister's Manor again.

23
00:01:08,700 --> 00:01:10,560
The top noble lady in the capital,

24
00:01:10,860 --> 00:01:12,330
and now you hold the title of Princess.

25
00:01:12,330 --> 00:01:14,000
You have a bright future ahead.

26
00:01:14,000 --> 00:01:16,860
Don't get involved with a prisoner like me anymore.

27
00:01:17,530 --> 00:01:18,860
Come closer.

28
00:01:21,830 --> 00:01:22,730
Why did you hit me?

29
00:01:22,730 --> 00:01:23,900
Lu Jingxing.

30
00:01:24,260 --> 00:01:26,860
How dare you think I, Shen Lvyi, am someone who despises the poor

31
00:01:26,860 --> 00:01:28,760
and changes sides with the wind?

32
00:01:31,160 --> 00:01:32,100
Lvyi.

33
00:01:32,630 --> 00:01:34,960
Say a few more words to me before you leave.

34
00:01:38,600 --> 00:01:40,900
Lu Jingxing is entirely loyal to Your Majesty.

35
00:01:40,900 --> 00:01:42,660
It was I who kept the edict from him.

36
00:01:42,660 --> 00:01:44,130
He was deceived by me.

37
00:01:44,130 --> 00:01:46,100
I beg Your Majesty to investigate thoroughly.

38
00:01:46,100 --> 00:01:46,900
Princess.

39
00:01:47,500 --> 00:01:48,960
You have a bright future.

40
00:01:49,960 --> 00:01:51,430
Why get mixed up with him?

41
00:01:52,800 --> 00:01:55,000
Your marriage was hasty to begin with.

42
00:01:55,430 --> 00:01:56,560
I can issue an edict

43
00:01:56,560 --> 00:01:57,890
to annul this marriage.

44
00:01:58,360 --> 00:01:59,000
No.

45
00:01:59,560 --> 00:02:00,360
Your Majesty.

46
00:02:00,800 --> 00:02:02,800
I will always be Lu Jingxing's wife.

47
00:02:03,100 --> 00:02:05,200
But I will never trust him again,

48
00:02:05,200 --> 00:02:06,900
nor will I give him an important position again.

49
00:02:06,900 --> 00:02:09,229
Lu Jingxing has no future anymore.

50
00:02:09,530 --> 00:02:11,260
Do you still want to be his wife?

51
00:02:11,860 --> 00:02:12,500
Yes.

52
00:02:14,260 --> 00:02:15,630
You are of noble birth,

53
00:02:15,630 --> 00:02:16,700
with excellent character.

54
00:02:16,700 --> 00:02:18,360
In the prime of your life,

55
00:02:18,360 --> 00:02:20,800
you'd waste your life with a useless man.

56
00:02:20,800 --> 00:02:22,630
Do you still want to be his wife?

57
00:02:26,130 --> 00:02:27,960
Why bother?

58
00:02:31,260 --> 00:02:32,060
Your Majesty.

59
00:02:33,300 --> 00:02:35,560
When I first favored Lu Jingxing,

60
00:02:35,560 --> 00:02:37,730
I just cherished his extraordinary talent,

61
00:02:37,730 --> 00:02:40,230
and didn't want to bury such a talented general.

62
00:02:40,230 --> 00:02:41,030
Later on.

63
00:02:41,660 --> 00:02:42,920
After years together,

64
00:02:43,160 --> 00:02:45,560
I was deeply attracted by his pure heart.

65
00:02:47,660 --> 00:02:49,530
My father has Your Majesty in his heart,

66
00:02:49,530 --> 00:02:51,400
national affairs and the people.

67
00:02:51,960 --> 00:02:55,160
My mother has my father and younger siblings in her heart.

68
00:02:55,460 --> 00:02:57,260
In this world, only Lu Jingxing,

69
00:02:57,260 --> 00:02:59,120
no matter what situation he is in,

70
00:02:59,730 --> 00:03:01,260
has only me in his heart.

71
00:03:02,630 --> 00:03:04,700
Even when I had to abandon him back then,

72
00:03:04,700 --> 00:03:06,160
and almost beat him to death,

73
00:03:06,160 --> 00:03:07,690
he never truly gave up on me.

74
00:03:08,760 --> 00:03:10,230
In my life, I, Shen Lvyi,

75
00:03:10,630 --> 00:03:11,960
will not fail my family,

76
00:03:12,000 --> 00:03:13,460
nor my righteous beliefs.

77
00:03:14,030 --> 00:03:15,760
I have only failed Lu Jingxing.

78
00:03:16,460 --> 00:03:17,720
For the rest of my life,

79
00:03:17,730 --> 00:03:19,390
I just want to stay by his side.

80
00:03:19,860 --> 00:03:21,720
No matter if he is a great general.

81
00:03:22,030 --> 00:03:23,500
Still a prisoner.

82
00:03:25,400 --> 00:03:26,700
Have you heard enough?

83
00:03:26,700 --> 00:03:27,660
Get out here!

84
00:03:31,900 --> 00:03:33,900
I thank Your Majesty for your grace.

85
00:03:34,660 --> 00:03:37,660
He was implicated in an embezzlement case in the army,

86
00:03:38,060 --> 00:03:40,360
but the authorities only questioned him routinely.

87
00:03:40,360 --> 00:03:42,660
He was to be released after they found he had nothing to do with it.

88
00:03:42,660 --> 00:03:43,860
But he

89
00:03:44,329 --> 00:03:47,360
put on this act to make you worry,

90
00:03:47,360 --> 00:03:49,800
just to hear what's in your heart.

91
00:03:51,000 --> 00:03:52,230
Don't be angry.

92
00:03:52,660 --> 00:03:54,800
The truth is, when you gave up on me three years ago,

93
00:03:54,800 --> 00:03:56,630
it left a huge shadow in my heart.

94
00:03:56,630 --> 00:03:57,760
I never felt secure.

95
00:03:59,100 --> 00:04:00,600
Do you feel secure now?

96
00:04:01,060 --> 00:04:01,800
Yes.

97
00:04:03,630 --> 00:04:04,360
Your Majesty,

98
00:04:04,360 --> 00:04:05,730
save my miserable life!

99
00:04:13,660 --> 00:04:16,060
In the autumn of the fourth year of Dasheng,

100
00:04:16,060 --> 00:04:17,930
the Northern Di invaded the border,

101
00:04:17,930 --> 00:04:19,730
burning, killing, and looting.

102
00:04:20,100 --> 00:04:23,330
The border of Dasheng was in imminent danger.

103
00:04:25,930 --> 00:04:29,500
General of Weibei, Lu Jingxing, requested to go to war.

104
00:04:36,860 --> 00:04:39,920
His wife, Shen Lvyi, resolutely accompanied the army.

105
00:04:42,560 --> 00:04:45,100
This expedition bears great responsibility.

106
00:04:45,100 --> 00:04:47,460
I order you to repel the Northern Di

107
00:04:47,860 --> 00:04:50,320
and protect the peace of our Dasheng border.

108
00:04:50,760 --> 00:04:52,060
I obey Your Majesty's decree.

109
00:04:52,060 --> 00:04:53,520
I will not fail my mission.

110
00:04:54,800 --> 00:04:57,130
Treat her well and don't be a jerk anymore.

111
00:04:57,230 --> 00:04:58,230
If you ask me,

112
00:04:58,560 --> 00:05:00,930
Miss Shen is smart and capable, no less than any man.

113
00:05:00,930 --> 00:05:03,100
She is even fit to be the Empress.

114
00:05:03,330 --> 00:05:04,330
Your Majesty,

115
00:05:04,330 --> 00:05:05,860
I have made great military contributions.

116
00:05:05,860 --> 00:05:08,060
I am also fit to be the founding emperor.

117
00:05:10,660 --> 00:05:11,830
Get lost!

118
00:05:12,500 --> 00:05:16,100
You are not allowed to come back until you have wiped out the Northern Di.

119
00:05:16,100 --> 00:05:17,260
Yes, sir.

120
00:05:30,460 --> 00:05:31,960
The enemy's left flank is weak.

121
00:05:31,960 --> 00:05:34,760
We can send an elite cavalry to flank them and attack from behind.

122
00:05:34,760 --> 00:05:36,430
It will definitely disrupt their formation.

123
00:05:36,430 --> 00:05:37,400
Good plan, strategist.

124
00:05:37,400 --> 00:05:38,630
We'll do as you say.

125
00:06:24,230 --> 00:06:25,760
For this victorious battle,

126
00:06:25,760 --> 00:06:27,420
you take the greatest credit.

127
00:06:28,130 --> 00:06:29,100
Half of this military merit

128
00:06:29,100 --> 00:06:30,060
belongs to you.

129
00:06:35,460 --> 00:06:36,860
I am so lucky in this life.

130
00:06:36,930 --> 00:06:38,600
After misunderstandings and separations,

131
00:06:38,600 --> 00:06:40,460
I finally have you to stay with me.

132
00:06:41,500 --> 00:06:43,430
I will protect the endless mountains and rivers,

133
00:06:43,430 --> 00:06:45,060
and give all my tenderness to you.

134
00:06:45,060 --> 00:06:46,720
I have no regrets in this life.

135
00:06:47,230 --> 00:06:49,600
I will find you again in the next life.
